lines.text: He's all upset and it's probably my fault.
Well, I'm pretty fuckin' upset and it's definitely your fault.
Hey Benario! My face is leaving in 5 minutes! Be on it!
Forget it! I'm not that drunk... well, not yet!
Does that mean we're done? Huh?
I've been good, havn't I? A good daughter. No complaints, no problems.

Everything's been just great. I've always had alot of friends, I don't do drugs, I've never had an abortion, I've never even had the measles. Is it true? It is true, isn't it? I've never even had the measles.
No! I don't want to calm down. I'm sick of calming down. I'm sick of everything being OK!
